name: MY MOTHER TURNED OUT TO BE MY FATHER 0602/2602
description:
Series 1
Take a Sip and Start Your (2022) Dreams 

For some, dreams are just wishes. A way of hearts telling us our deepest desire and fear. But for others, dreams are prominent. It is believed to be a guidance. A vision to the future. 

As an Indonesian yourself, you must be aware of Togel. Our very own betting culture that promises fantastic money prizes. To win the game, one must put 2-4 numbers on the gambling coupons based on one's intuition. Many believe that these numbers appear in dreams, as a way of the future revealing itself. A dream becomes a divine intervention. A sign so supernatural we believe in magic. 

So what's your dream? In a year full of uncertainty, be mindful to determine your next steps to reach that dream. Rather than betting at risk, here's something better to put your mind at ease. Open this pack, make your coffee, take a sip and get started.

May all your 2022 dreams come true.
